In this assignment we will cover threads,POSIX thread api.

1>> Write a program to create a thread in main thread and see the O/P
    of top and ps corresponding to that thread and state your observtion.

2>> Write a program to have two child process from a parent process
    and create a thread from each thread.

3>> In the above program have one shared resource or a global structure
    and try to update the structure from one thread and read from other
    thread.

4>> Try to synchronize the threads using MUTEX.
